title: Mr Peabody and Sherman : Wabac Adventures Disc 1
description:
Mr. Peabody and Sherman Wabac Adventures Disc 1

Meet Mr. Peabody, the worlds smartest dog and the genius behind the WABAC machine ... a device that allows Mr. Peabody and his pet boy Sherman to travel back in time!! Join the unlikely duo's adventures as they leave their mark on monumental events and keep history from becoming ... well History...

10 Episodes are included:

Christopher Columbus
Captain Matthew Clift
Captain Kidd
Leif Ericsson
Ferdinand Magellan
Francisco Pizzaro
Marco Polo
Ponce de Leon
Vasco Nunez de Balboa
Zebulon Pike
